    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Coming this Fall! A new jet age travel experience!\nElectra/Flight\nThe New Lockheed Electra\nwill bring you a totally differ-\nent air travel experience - you'll\nfly faster than ever before…yet\nin vibration-free, relaxing quiet!\nSave 25% in time over today's\ninter-city schedules.\nYou choose from more frequent\nElectra/ Flights... leaving from\ntoday's close-in airports...taking\njet age air travel even to smaller\ncommunities. (The Electra can\nserve over 300 existing commer-\ncial airports in the U.S. alone.)\nOn board, you feel at home imme-\ndiately in \"living room\" comfort.\nElectra cabins are wider, more spa-\ncious. Your seat is roomier, more\nrelaxing-you look through a big\n\"picture window,\" or stroll a broad\naisle to enjoy a friendly lounge.\nLook for the jet with props\nThe big General Motors Allison\nProp-jet Engines are turning over.\n(Note there's no quiver-no\nshake!) These 4 giants are jet\nturbine engines (for power and\nspeed) combined with 4-bladed\nprops (for more dependable\nshort-flight performance).\nIn the air you speed along in\nserene smoothness. If \"weather\"\nis sighted or radar-sensed ahead,\nyour pilot can choose the best alti-\ntude or course for your comfort...\nabove or below storms or winds.\nYou can depend on scheduled\narrival and departure times.\nWhen Electra descends for landing -\nrelax. The big props actually act like\n\"brakes\"\nagainst the air for short,\nsafe landings even on slick runways.\nYou disembark near terminals and\ncan carry your luggage for quicker\ngetaway.\nYou will enjoy Electra/ Flight on these leading airlines:\nANSETTANA\nWROTERN\nThe finest jet age airliner for city-to-city travel LOCKHEED ELECTRA\nLockheed Aircraft Corporation, Burbank, California\nAeronaves de Mexico\namerican nirtnes\nBraniff Airways\nCathay-Pacific Airways.\nEastern Air Lines\naruda indonesian airways\nKLM Royal Dutch Airlines\nVational Airanes\nPSA-Pacific Southwest\nAirlines\nWester Airlines\nJULY 1958\n17"
